            h3 Tile status > badge
            p
              | A badge can display either a number from 1-99 or a status glyph. badge is positioned in tile status container on the bottom right corner.
              | Metro UI CSS support main Windows 8 badges:
              span.fg-color-blue
                | activity, alert, available, away, busy, newMessage, paused, playing, unavailable, error and attention
              | as built-in. Default badge background color is blue but may be changed, example with built-in classes
              code .bg-color-*
              | .
